						<summary>

						<p>This seems to record a gift of land after purchase for offerings during the early morning service in the temple of Pāṇdīśuramuḍaiya-Nāyaṉār at Āḻvāṉkōil in Aṇḍanāḍu by one Śrī Parañjōti Sūryadēvaṉ of Kāñaiyirukkai Śōḻaṇallūr of Pāṇḍimaṇḍalam. </p>						

